name: DealSniper
0:
”Alexa, ask deal sniper does chipotle have any offers”
”Alexa, ask deal sniper are there any coupons for qdoba”
”Alexa, ask deal sniper are there any deals at denny's”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: deal sniper
des:
Deal Sniper uses real time data to check if the brand you ask for currently has any offers, coupons or deals. It's easy to get started! You do not to take any steps on your side like creating an account. Just launch the app and ask for a deal.

No pre-requisite hardware needed, just launch and ask away.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
